    {
      "id": "1320871568979885",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Very Underrated Game",
      "review_description": "When it comes to VR games, you're left with some pretty basic stuff that can get boring very easily. That couldn't be further from the truth when it comes to Troop VR. This absolute masterpiece of a game never seems to get boring, and it's a wonderful way to engage with others and make new friends. The game design and thought process that went into this is unmatched, especially since this game comes from an experienced game developer who is known to have made incredible games like Noclip VR. In fact, I've actually known the owner for well over a year online, and what makes his games stand out is that they never seem to get too boring, and when an update comes out, it's always thrilling and exciting to play. Whenever there's a bug, he doesn't hesitate to try and fix it right away, and that's what makes these games so good.\n\nI hope this review helped you, and how it's amazing to have a game this well made for absolutely free! Definitely 5 stars, hands down.",
      "date": 1742624301,
      "review_helpful_count": 32,
      "author_display_name": "ChoobVR",
      "author_alias": "ChoobVR",
      "developer_response": null
